_sText: A fun map that has 2 player cannons, 2 different teleports and 4 total teleports (youll have to find them) also it has 6 tripwires. 44 player slots. This is the first release of this map so please DL it and tell what I can do to make it more fun :D Some custom textures were used along with standard textures. I think the NAV file is included. Spinning thing in middle does 5 dmg/sec. There is also an unfolding tower. Also there is no fall damage. You can find the prefab for the laser bridge here Needs one more assessment!!!! Prefabs: Corner Stairs - Ruff Tron Crate - JLM Unfolding tower v2 - NAK93 Dev_building - Demonsoul1616 awsome human canon - smurfii Weidey's Tripline - Weidey
